{
  "stem": "26111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About three months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That makes it four months, doesn't it? 10th of-- we would arrive there 11th or 12th of December, '38, and-- I can find out the exact-- but it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Three and a half months, or so, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Four months, maybe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some rudimentary English lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in fact, the few of us that knew English, like I did, volunteered to give some English lessons to those that had none at all.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were given some books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was very, very partial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you know, we weren't teachers and hardly knew the language well enough to teach it to others.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was better than nothing, I imagine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It made them feel a little bit that they could get around on their own, without-- without being total idiots.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think it did some good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there was some self-help going on, in this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was one very touching incident that I, I wanted to just quickly mention.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a girls boarding school nearby-- a very posh girls boarding school-- that for Christmas holidays, was of course empty, because all the, all the girls were, were-- had gone home.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the directors of the school invited the children from the camp to, to go there and spend the Christmas holidays.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think we were allowed to go for a week, because there weren't many more children in the camp than, than the school could take.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Although it was a fairly big school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I got-- that, that was a very nice experience.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because it got us in touch-- we each had notes, when we went to the rooms-- our bedrooms-- that were the girls' bedrooms.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
